{"tid":1801501,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 周柏豪真係好撚廢","createTime":"2019-12-28T16:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T16:20:00.000Z","uid":165817,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6545c4bb4186afb30d291e3a254f5ef6dca7be03","tid":1801501,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"真係好撚廢 睇到中立球迷都炆<br />\n下下都上腳 以為自己好好波<br />\n但技術又唔係突出<br />\n腳腳都扭但又唔扭得 場場都斷幾廿次纜<br />\n<br />\n維拉而家喺降班區唔係冇原因<br />\n好多球權去到佢度即刻斷<br />\n仲要輸緊俾屈福特 佢踢到成pat屎咁<br />\n之前仲試過連續20場英超輸波 破咗歷史紀錄<br />\n<br />\n降班之前講到咩超新星<br />\n幾年之後上返嚟 完全冇進步<br />\n但上腳仲多咗 扮哂球星咁<br />\n似柏豪真係大哂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66296b83fddcb6caf012f27854c0c3e4f7463dfc","tid":1801501,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"話口未完 啱啱輸十二碼呢球 又係基亞利殊喺中場交失"},{"pid":"f7c494c291e0ad7d7e692bcfb7e1e356a221e039","tid":1801501,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800386</a>"},{"pid":"fdf4f5b06fa72299d812fe459fc3b3cce8326000","tid":1801501,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:24:23.000Z","msg":"黑氣石<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca2e2eafe0b8b3e58a9e0367815f67137c2641d","tid":1801501,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdf4f5b06fa72299d812fe459fc3b3cce8326000","tid":1801501,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:24:23.000Z","msg":"黑氣石<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"連續20場出佢都輸波<br />\n呢啲根本已經唔係邪唔邪嘅問題<br />\n係好科學 好理性嘅事實嚟 就係佢確實令維拉斷咗好多纜<br />\n<br />\n同佢呢啲表演慾極強又唔係好波嘅人做隊友 真係喊三聲"},{"pid":"efe2e9362831ed051e77622c786dcf183632136f","tid":1801501,"ui